00:43:15.919 --> 00:43:22.080
And one thing to note, we've talked a lot about documents and things like that, but

00:43:23.600 --> 00:43:28.000
there are several formats in Cordo that are supported by brand.yaml.

00:43:28.000 --> 00:43:29.600
So this is a web page.

00:43:29.600 --> 00:43:34.399
